Package com.Scheduling.Web.App.models

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
com.Scheduling.Web.App.models.BaseEntity
com.Scheduling.Web.App.models.Appointment
public class Appointment extends BaseEntity
The Appointment class is responsible for storing all variables associated with any specific appointment. It extends the BaseEntity class to include the ID, createdDate, updatedDate, createdBy, and lastUpdatedBy variables by utilizing inheritance of the BaseEntity class instance variables and methods.
